In an effort to boost economic growth and retain residents who would otherwise pursue a more exciting and lucrative lifestyle in other areas, Iowa state officials unveiled a new population retention campaign Thursday designed to appeal to younger Iowans’ sense of filial piety with the slogan “The Stress Will Kill Your Mother.” “We hope this campaign sells our native sons and daughters on the Hawkeye State by reminding them just how much pain their departure would cause the woman who gave birth to them.